    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It's been such a great car for me and is still in really solid shape! It\u2019s super dependable, drives smoothly, and is ready for many more miles of adventures. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a quality vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and let you take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and upgraded Bilstein dampers, providing exceptional lateral grip and feedback. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. A true driver's car with the mechanical pedigree to match.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Minimal exterior wear. Runs smooth. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained Audi S5 combines exhilarating performance with daily-driver reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, showing only the lightest road peppering on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up chip on the driver-side door. Inside, the Nappa leather seats remain supple with minimal bolster wear, and the cabin remains a smoke-free environment where every button and digital display functions perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle shines; it has followed a strict maintenance schedule with a documented history of synthetic oil changes and a recent comprehensive brake service. The turbocharged V6 pulls strongly without hesitation, and the Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides confident, planted handling. It sits on a set of premium performance tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a turn-key example for the discerning buyer who values a balanced history of documented care and spirited performance.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic preservation. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. An ideal acquisition for those seeking a balance of sophisticated engineering and proven longevity.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more adventures? This car is in such solid shape and drives like a dream! It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of character from its travels, but honestly, it\u2019s been super reliable and well-taken care of. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a high-quality vehicle without paying those sky-high showroom prices. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin and see how smooth it feels for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically sound, with the critical VANOS system recently overhauled and valve clearances adjusted to factory specifications. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and a functional M-Variable differential lock, ensuring the 333hp is delivered effectively to the tarmac. While the finish shows minor stone chipping and interior bolster wear consistent with 'good' condition, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A communicative hydraulic steering rack and a well-sorted suspension geometry make this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking an analog driving experience without the 'mint' premium.",
      "price": 33800.0,
